Available Tools: list_inventory | restock_item | get_low_stock | update_price
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "slot_id": "string", "quantity": number, "price": number }
Response Schema: { "inventory": [{ "slot_id": "string", "name": "string", "quantity": number, "price": number }] }
---
Question: Identify which products are critically low in the library breakroom dispenser.
Call: { "func_call": "get_low_stock", "slot_id": "", "quantity": 0, "price": 0 }
Response: { "inventory": [{ "slot_id": "J1", "name": "Green Tea", "quantity": 1, "price": 1.30 }, { "slot_id": "J2", "name": "Rice Cake", "quantity": 2, "price": 0.95 }] }

Question: Modify the cost of the Espresso Shot in slot K5 to $4.00 following a vendor rate hike.
Call: { "func_call": "update_price", "slot_id": "K5", "quantity": 0, "price": 4.00 }
Response: { "inventory": [{ "slot_id": "K5", "name": "Espresso Shot", "quantity": 11, "price": 4.00 }] }

Question: Display the full inventory list for the subway station kiosk.
Call: { "func_call": "list_inventory", "slot_id": "", "quantity": 0, "price": 0 }
